20columnist%20says%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20financial%20promise%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20they're%20not%20happy%20about%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGot%20a%20question%20for%20our%20columnist%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20daughter%2C%20who%20is%2020%2C%20recently%20became%20engaged%20to%20her%20high%20school%20sweetheart.%20They%20are%20planning%20a%20wedding%20for%20summer%202026.%20She%20expects%20me%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20wedding%20like%20I%20always%20promised%2C%20but%20I%20think%20getting%20married%20this%20young%20is%20a%20huge%20mistake%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20help%20her%20make.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHer%20father%20and%20I%20also%20met%20in%20high%20school%2C%20married%20young%2C%20had%20two%20kids%2C%20and%20then%20divorced%20after%20I%20learned%20he%20had%20been%20serially%20unfaithful.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20a%20lot%20of%20hindsight%20and%20healing%2C%20I've%20realized%20that%20while%20my%20ex%20ended%20our%20marriage%20with%20his%20choices%2C%20we%20were%20both%20too%20young%2C%20immature%2C%20and%20inexperienced%20for%20it%20to%20have%20ever%20lasted.%20I%20wanted%20to%20play%20house%2C%20and%20didn't%20care%20who%20I%20did%20it%20with.%20He%20wanted%20to%20play%20the%20field%2C%20and%20a%20wedding%20ring%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20stop%20him.%20We%20were%20both%20too%20young%20to%20know%20who%20we%20were%20and%20what%20we%20needed.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20tried%20sharing%20this%20story%20with%20my%20daughter%2C%20but%20all%20she%20seems%20to%20hear%20is%20that%20I%20hate%20her%20fianc%C3%A9.%20I%20think%20he's%20a%20nice%20enough%20guy%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20him%20I%20take%20issue%20with.%20It's%20how%20young%20they%20are.%20I've%20promised%20to%20give%20her%20%2410%2C000%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20her%20wedding%20for%20years%2C%20but%20now%20that%20feels%20like%20a%20high%20price%20for%20what%20I%20truly%20believe%20will%20be%20the%20worst%20mistake%20of%20her%20life.%20What%20should%20I%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mom%20with%20Misgivings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Misgivings%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMistakes%20are%20tricky%20things.%20You%20regret%20marrying%20so%20young%2C%20but%20if%20Rumplestiltskin%20appeared%20on%20your%20doorstep%20and%20offered%20you%20a%20do-over%20that%20wiped%20your%20children%20from%20existence%2C%20my%20guess%20is%2C%20you'd%20turn%20him%20down%20flat.%20You%20and%20your%20ex%20would%20likely%20both%20undo%20his%20infidelity%20if%20you%20could%2C%20but%20then%20you'd%20still%20be%20trapped%20in%20an%20unhappy%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMistakes%20can%20range%20from%20Bob%20Ross's%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20little%20accidents%26quot%3B%20to%20devastating%20tragedies%2C%20but%20they%20all%20become%20part%20of%20our%20stories.%20They%20alter%20our%20lives%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20around%20us.%20If%20we%20never%20made%20any%20mistakes%2C%20we%20would%20have%20less%20of%20everything%2C%20including%20the%20necessary%20experience%20to%20recognize%20and%20avoid%20future%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20parents%2C%20we%20want%20to%20do%20that%20part%20for%20our%20kids.%20We%20want%20to%20struggle%20through%20tough%20consequences%20so%20they%20never%20have%20to.%20Sometimes%20this%20works.%20Sometimes%20our%20cautionary%20tales%20and%20wise%20counsel%20get%20through%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20never%20have%20to%20experience%20the%20pain%20we%20endured.%20Other%20times%2C%20they%20have%20to%20make%20their%20own%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20children%20are%20living%20out%20their%20own%20stories%20full%20of%20twists%20and%20turns%2C%20magnificent%20triumphs%2C%20happy%20accidents%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20though%20as%20a%20mother%2C%20my%20stomach%20twists%20even%20writing%20this%2C%20devastating%20tragedies.%20Sometimes%20they%20will%20lose%2C%20sometimes%20they%20will%20win%2C%20but%20it%20was%20always%20their%20game%20to%20play.%20Not%20ours.%20We're%20the%20fans%20cheering%20on%20the%20sidelines.%20Our%20children%20deserve%20to%20live%20full%20lives%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bfull%26quot%3B%20includes%20even%20the%20hard%20parts%20of%20being%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20reminded%20of%20gymnast%20Aly%20Raisman's%20parents'%20viral%20behavior%20during%20the%202012%20Olympics.%20Up%20in%20the%20stands%2C%20they%20swayed%20and%20squirmed%20and%20winced%20with%20every%20step%20in%20their%20talented%20daughter's%20complex%20routine.%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20sacrifices%20they%20made%20to%20get%20Aly%20on%20that%20stage%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20London%20Olympics%2C%20among%20the%20elite%20of%20the%20elite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20they%20were%20a%20middle-aged%20couple%20sitting%20in%20stadium%20seats%20and%20wearing%20jeans%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%2C%20as%20they%20watched%20their%20daughter%2C%20their%20consciousnesses%20left%20their%20bodies%20and%20joined%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20launched%20her%20body%20over%20the%20vault%2C%20they%20leaned%20back%20in%20their%20seats%2C%20eyes%20full%20of%20profound%20empathy%2C%20and%20still%2C%20Aly%20alone%20flew%20through%20the%20air%20and%20stuck%20her%20landing.%20Not%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20truest%2C%20hardest%20part%20of%20parenting%20%E2%80%94%20letting%20go.%20Remembering%20that%20our%20kids'%20lives%20belong%20to%20them%2C%20not%20us.%20This%20includes%20their%20successes%2C%20failures%2C%20joy%2C%20and%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20give%20your%20daughter%20your%20blessing%2