0and%20fiction.%20Listen%20to%20lived%20experiences.%20Talk%20to%20someone.%20Support%20organisations%20working%20in%20the%20mental%20health%20space.%20Small%20steps%20like%20respectful%20language%20can%20help%20chip%20away%20at%20decades%20of%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20when%20we%20choose%20to%20understand%2C%20we%20give%20people%20more%20than%20treatment%20%E2%80%94%20we%20offer%20them%20dignity%2C%20connection%2C%20and%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748169000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D437497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20if%20everything%20you%20knew%20about%20schizophrenia%20was%20wrong%3F%20This%20article%20gently%20peels%20back%20the%20layers%20of%20stigma%2C%20with%20a%20psychologist%20explaining%20the%20truths%20behind%20a%20misunderstood%20mental%20illness.%20Through%20warmth%20and%20clarity%2C%20it%20urges%20us%20to%20rethink%20assumptions%20and%20respond%20with%20compassion%20rather%20than%20fear.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea%20detains%203%20officials%20following%20botched%20warship%20launch%2C%20state%20media%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221167%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satellite%20imagery%20shows%20a%20North%20Korean%20warship%20partially%20covered%20with%20blue%20tarps%20after%20a%20failed%20launch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6832db9ac6ad288d1481de2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22833%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESatellite%20imagery%20showed%20a%20North%20Korean%20warship%20partially%20covered%20with%20blue%20tarps%20after%20a%20failed%20launch.%3Cp%3EMaxar%20%2F%20