2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20could%20deter%20Bhaskar%20from%20going%20after%20what%20he%20wanted%2C%20not%20even%20his%20trigeminal%20neuralgia%20(a%20condition%20sudden%2C%20intense%2C%20electric%20shock-like%20pain%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20face).%20In%20his%2070s%2C%20while%20heading%20to%20South%20Reef%20Island%20in%20North%20Andaman%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F63528%2Fmysterious-facts-andaman-nicobar-islands%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevastated%20in%202004%20by%20a%20tsunami%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20the%20island%20where%20Bhaskar%20had%20previously%20initiated%20a%20monitoring%20programme%20for%20hawksbill%20turtles%20%E2%80%94%20the%20boat%20journey%20was%20proving%20too%20hazardous.%20It%20did%20not%20take%20more%20than%20an%20instant%20for%20Bhaskar%20to%20don%20his%20fins%20and%20enter%20the%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhitaker%20is%20not%20surprised.%20He%20got%20a%20front%20row%20seat%20to%20Bhaskar%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20adventure%20and%20going%20the%20extra%20mile%2C%20while%20the%20two%20often%20interacted%20during%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Madras%20Snake%20Park%2C%20quite%20near%20to%20IIT%20Madras%20where%20Bhaskar%20was%20studying.%20In%20fact%20Bhaskar%20is%20said%20to%20have%20spent%20more%20time%20swimming%20in%20the%20waters%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20than%20in%20the%20classroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_xX0J9IwgA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_xX0J9IwgA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3